Deemos tapped his foot waiting for Kluster to let him have Gangon. Rizopas =
seen Plintissa crying and hiding in a corner.

"Sorry if I scared you." Riz=
opas says. Stronghold and Blender were counting up some money. Serge realiz=
ed that he must consume to build power. He left outside to hunt. Doom Ice w=
as curious and followed him. Testifier was practicing his lines, the lines =
he was going to use before killing KitKat. And Gangon rots in his cell some=
 more, suffering from insomnia and the lack of brainpower to enter repair m=
ode. (Couldn't resist.)...
